      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's helpful. i also read something about how they used IQ-style testing or psychometric data to rank different groups. could you explain how they interpreted those test scores to argue that some races were naturally more \"advanced\" in civilization or social organization compared to others? i'm trying to capture the exact way they linked those scores to their worldview.",
